"body":"","statusCode":200,"responseHeaders":{"server":"nginx","date":"Sat, 18 Apr 2026 09:19:35 GMT","content-type":"application/json;charset=utf-8","content-length":"10447","connection":"close","x-backend-host":"0725:4000","x-gateway-host":"6c32dde15b3ccfa1cbc62357d4c35a2f5eb4523ceae6af616a99b7b71728704f7305b76bd04138e0c333119448529342"},"responseBody":"{\"ret\":0,\"requestId\":\"1776503974aa498144140ef297\",\"timestamp\":1776503975407,\"result\":{\"elements\":[{\"dataType\":\"dramaSearchList\",\"showTitle\":false,\"hasMore\":false,\"contents\":[{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":679764,\"duanjuId\":\"hbEpisodes0000000000000000000283\",\"title\":\"<tag>女人的</tag>故事\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://img-cdn.youlishipin.com/2025/05/29/fc131565487a3db63bbe2a477388daaa.jpg\",\"desc\":\"路上捡的小孩,竟是我打开高光人生的钥匙?为替母亲复仇,直接把仇人一家子都拖下水。\",\"total\":88,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"huabo\",\"categories\":[\"现代\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\",\"mandatoryAdTime\":0,\"duanjuType\":1,\"jumpUrl\":\"\",\"tag\":\"\",\"tagColor\":\"\",\"tags\":\"逆袭,情感\",\"videoMaterialType\":0,\"dramaUuid\":679764,\"playViewText\":\"17.2万\",\"bingeWatchNumber\":2905,\"missingEpisode\":false,\"actorList\":[{\"name\":\"李浩\"},{\"name\":\"赵敏\"}]}},{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":713559,\"duanjuId\":\"lihunhoudenvrdyb\",\"title\":\"离婚后<tag>的女人</tag>\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://xifan.heytapimage.com/iot-duanju-public-hn1/duanju/cp360/lihunhoudenvrdyb/image/9536adfecc0a1c5b139c05218b5dace1_1761710744.png?x-amz-process=image/format,webp/quality,Q_20\",\"desc\":\"故事主要围绕着女主角在婚礼前夕与未婚夫分手的故事展开。女主角突然发现了未婚夫的不忠行为，被背叛的痛苦迫使她做出了艰难的决定。在分手后，她开始重新审视自己的价值和人生目标，展开一段个人成长的旅程。\",\"total\":11,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"cp360\",\"categories\":[\"虐恋\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\",\"mandatoryAdTime\":0,\"duanjuType\":1,\"jumpUrl\":\"\",\"tag\":\"\",\"tagColor\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\",\"videoMaterialType\":0,\"dramaUuid\":713559,\"playViewText\":\"8.1万\",\"bingeWatchNumber\":1757,\"missingEpisode\":false,\"actorList\":[{\"name\":\"徐振宇\"},{\"name\":\"刘雯子\"}]}},{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":722761,\"duanjuId\":\"8984\",\"title\":\"<tag>不</tag>能恋爱<tag>的女人</tag>\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://xifan.heytapimage.com/iot-duanju-public-hn1/duanju/jiuzhou/8984/image/b16fdda59955c0075fd54f1996287ec1_1773998987.jpeg?x-amz-process=image/format,webp/quality,Q_20\",\"desc\":\"颜薇是坐拥百w粉丝的情感博主，帮助很多朋友和粉丝解决感情问题。同时也是朋友圈里响当当的“虐渣女王”，帮助闺蜜们出气惩罚渣男。她在惩罚感情背叛者的过程中，遇到了情感障碍的云深，两人互相帮助互相治愈，最终明白了什么是真爱。\",\"total\":12,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"jiuzhou\",\"categories\":[\"都市\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\",\"mandatoryAdTime\":0,\"duanjuType\":1,\"jumpUrl\":\"\",\"tag\":\"\",\"tagColor\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\",\"videoMaterialType\":0,\"dramaUuid\":722761,\"playViewText\":\"5.6万\",\"bingeWatchNumber\":1316,\"missingEpisode\":false,\"actorList\":[{\"name\":\"王梓豪\"},{\"name\":\"王嘉宁\"}]}},{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":687532,\"duanjuId\":\"yangbushudenrslb\",\"title\":\"<tag>这是女人</tag>\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://img-cdn.youlishipin.com/2025/07/16/63801c3f2d4dcc1c0a5552c691f00625.jpg\",\"desc\":\"叶天大学时对秦亦晴一见钟情，主动告白和秦亦晴在一起。但交往八年，秦亦晴还是跟她的男闺蜜纠缠不清，叶天为此一次又一次地与秦亦晴争吵，终于在求婚当天，秦亦晴又被张翰之叫走后，叶天死心了……\",\"total\":40,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"cp360\",\"categories\":[\"复仇\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\",\"mandatoryAdTime\":0,\"duanjuType\":1,\"jumpUrl\":\"\",\"tag\":\"\",\"tagColor\":\"\",\"tags\":\"\",\"videoMaterialType\":0,\"dramaUuid\":687532,\"playViewText\":\"213.3万\",\"bingeWatchNumber\":7805,\"missingEpisode\":false,\"actorList\":[{\"name\":\"冯伊洋\"},{\"name\":\"张思琦\"}]}},{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":719725,\"duanjuId\":\"hbEpisodes0000000000000000001251\",\"title\":\"我<tag>的</tag>将军大<tag>人</tag>\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://img-cdn.youlishipin.com/2026/01/15/7835dd37430f3d5c40f0c12a63751351.jpg\",\"desc\":\"方明意与沈卿卿本是古代相恋的恋人，第一世沈卿卿为救方明意被剑刺死，却因皇帝的诅咒重生；第二世两人再度相遇相爱，沈卿卿又为保护他遭枪击离世；第三世重逢时，方明意抢先救下沈卿卿，沈卿卿主动展开热烈追求，两人再续前缘，后续方明意为守护沈卿卿耗尽心力一夜白头，好在爱情的结晶降临拯救了他，最终一家三口相守相伴，收获圆满幸福。\",\"total\":78,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"huabo\",\"categories\":[\"甜宠\",\"都市\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\",\"mandatoryAdTime\":0,\"duanjuType\":1,\"jumpUrl\":\"\",\"tag\":\"\",\"tagColor\":\"\",\"tags\":\"甜宠,都市\",\"videoMaterialType\":0,\"dramaUuid\":719725,\"playViewText\":\"8.8万\",\"bingeWatchNumber\":1239,\"missingEpisode\":false,\"actorList\":[{\"name\":\"于尚煦\"}]}},{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":670024,\"duanjuId\":\"hbEpisodes0000000000000000000005\",\"title\":\"总裁达<tag>人的</tag>专属保镖\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://img-cdn.youlishipin.com/2025/04/28/59011c3db66a77a933da3f57a2961a9b.jpg\",\"desc\":\"名震世界的传奇王者低调回归都市，化身为美女总裁的贴身保镖。 一个妖孽如谜的男人，武功高强，医术精湛。 一群形形色色的女人，风姿绰约，美艳绝伦。 且看一代王者再战江湖，登巅峰，掌生死，掀起一番腥风血雨！\",\"total\":81,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"huabo\",\"categories\":[\"现代\",\"豪门恩怨\",\"都市\",\"扮猪吃虎\",\"打脸虐渣\",\"隐藏大佬\",\"豪门\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\",\"mandatoryAdTime\":0,\"duanjuType\":1,\"jumpUrl\":\"\",\"tag\":\"\",\"tagColor\":\"\",\"tags\":\"都市,逆袭\",\"videoMaterialType\":0,\"dramaUuid\":670024,\"playViewText\":\"112.7万\",\"bingeWatchNumber\":7014,\"missingEpisode\":false,\"actorList\":[{\"name\":\"江海娜\"},{\"name\":\"林琳\"},{\"name\":\"陈彬彬\"},{\"name\":\"宋斌\"}]}},{\"type\":[\"duanju\"],\"duanjuVo\":{\"id\":697064,\"duanjuId\":\"hbEpisodes0000000000000000000450\",\"title\":\"<tag>你的</tag>芬芳\",\"coverImageUrl\":\"https://img-cdn.youlishipin.com/2025/08/11/780d109b7d07755f6ee216717f1e0d1e.jpg\",\"desc\":\"在时尚繁华的都市，林暮深热爱香水创作，生活被创作与时尚活动填满，虽看似光鲜，却在追寻能触动灵魂的独特香气。一次时尚晚宴上，他与沈星瑶擦肩而过，她身上的独特体香开启了他的灵感。他主动接近，两人渐生情愫。同行嫉妒使绊，沈星瑶的过往也带来考验，但他们携手面对。林暮深将情感融入创作，用香水证明实力，也陪沈星瑶走出过去，最终收获事业巅峰与美好爱情。\",\"total\":90,\"updateStatus\":\"over\",\"source\":\"huabo\",\"categories\":[\"甜宠\",\"现代言情\"],\"status\":\"up\",\"preloadAdCount\":0,\"adPositions\":\"\